00:00:49.390 --> 00:00:54.329
Feeling good means we spend more, so casinos
cash in on dopamine at every turn.

00:00:54.329 --> 00:00:59.030
Numerous studies say more arousal means more
gambling, and faster music paired with flashing

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:03.079
