00:01:40.410 --> 00:01:42.560
architecture
Even the architecture has evolved.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:45.259
I find this particularly fascinating.

00:01:45.259 --> 00:01:49.970
Originally casinos focused on "gaming design:"
all the slot machines and tables were lined

00:01:49.970 --> 00:01:52.930
up, all together in a maze-like configuration.

00:01:52.930 --> 00:01:57.090
It was thought that this design would make
us step up and gamble at every turn.

00:01:57.090 --> 00:02:02.259
But based on scientific studies, casino design
has been radically redefined.

00:02:02.259 --> 00:02:07.729
New casinos are based on the idea of "adult
playgrounds" with high-ceilings and expansive,

00:02:07.729 --> 00:02:12.200
opulent, easy-to-navigate spaces; the Bellagio
is the quintessential example.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:16.560
Old-style casinos famously avoid windows and
clocks to help gamblers lose their sense of

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:21.120
place and time, but "playground" casinos make
people feel happy and comfortable, with sunshine,

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:25.610
high-ceilings and art; keeping us gambling,
having fun, and spending that money.

00:02:25.610 --> 00:02:30.950
A study published in the journal Environment
&amp; Behavior proved that this is working.

00:02:30.950 --> 00:02:33.970
People like the playground design, especially
women.

00:02:33.970 --> 00:02:38.319
In the compact "gaming design" women felt
crowded by others around them, if they were

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:41.660
too close to other people they'd gamble less.

00:02:41.660 --> 00:02:45.690
The adult playground design mitigates these
problems, and women now gamble even more.

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:49.819
Slots, for example, are historically very
popular with women, and revenue increased

00:02:49.819 --> 00:02:51.720
over 30 percent since 1970.

00:02:51.720 --> 00:02:57.660
It turns out, adding windows, bright colors,
and a resort feel, has a huge payoff for the

00:02:57.660 --> 00:02:58.660
House.

00:02:58.660 --> 00:03:02.959
The research showed, gamblers in a resort
playground casino feel more comfortable and

00:03:02.959 --> 00:03:04.970
